koromiko
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Hebe</i> spp, esp. <i>H salicifolia </i>(formerly <i>Veronica</i>), a large group of shrubs and small trees, found throughout NZ


Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: various early spellings
